original_title: Girls to Fight For - Womens Pro Wrestling Documentary
overview: PWA Studios celebrated International Womens Day 2020 by extending the stories of Australia's top female wrestlers in this documentary piece, Girls to Fight For.  Hear the perspectives of Australia's top female performers, from those who started this year to those who began over a decade ago.  Starring:  Madison Eagles - Pro Wrestler  Shazza McKenzie  Jessica Troy  Xena  Kingsley - Pro Wrestler  Cherry Stephens  Frankie B
title: Girls to Fight For - Womens Pro Wrestling Documentary
